message:
kia me ne ap se duty ki types pouchi hai
ap ka jawab me ne accept kiya to ap b mera jawab accept kar le
Software ka kam karta ho to web application banata ho ap kia duty karte hai
Ap ka nam jan sakta ho kia
Location ap ki kaha se hai
Allah ka karam hai or kam kesa chal raha hai karachi kab chakar laga rahe hai boss
pateri bakri k do bache lene ho to us k kia price hai
Pewer or Cross donu k rate bata de
Cross gabban bakri k kia rate hai fresh 2 dant ki bakri
ap k waha mandi kab lagti hai
Shera Print ki bakri gabban kitne tak ki mile gi
Mall kesa mile ga waha or rate kese hote hai waha ap kis city se hai
Kharidari abi karna behter hai ya muharram k bad
Shahdadpur karachi se ziada fasle per hai kia or agar karachi se waha ana chahye to kia gari mil jati hai or waha se karachi k liye asani se gari mil jati hai
Hafta or Itwar kon si sindh ki mandi lagti hai
Abbu se bat kar k batata ho ap ko
Sindhri mandi kis taraf hai or waha janwar kesa hota hai
Mirpurkhas  ki mandi kab lagti hai or ye kis taraf lagti hai
